Introduction

Yuju (Korean: 유주; Japanese: ユジュ) is a South Korean singer, rapper and actress under FNC Entertainment and FNC W.. She was a member and the Lead Vocalist, Rapper, and Visual of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet.

On January 21, 2019, she made her official debut as a member of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet with the single mini album "Let's Play Cherry Bullet" with "Q & A" serving as the title track.

On January 14, 2021, she's make her acting debut in the web drama Be My Boyfriend.
